{"title":"将军和士兵","authors":["权正"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军和士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"权正"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经理帽上没有军徽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经理肩上没有金星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，每当他来到工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建筑工人们仍然叫他将军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一次经理假意鼓起嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指着工作证向大伙申明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“祖国早把我改了行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也早已不是士兵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泥工来到经理面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着搅杆行持枪礼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“建设和战斗都是一个样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们仍然是祖国的士兵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“将军”和“士兵”们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被说得纵声大笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起闪亮的军功章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他们胸前叮当不停。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}